Third-party components
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This evaluation code is built on the inference framework of Tongyi DeepResearch:

    https://github.com/Alibaba-NLP/DeepResearch
    Copyright (c) Alibaba-NLP. Licensed under the Apache License 2.0.

The following files originate from DeepResearch's `inference/` and `evaluation/`
directories and are modified here (e.g. tool endpoints, URL filtering, and the
experience-injection variant); they remain under the Apache License 2.0 (see
LICENSE.deepresearch):

    react_agent.py, run_multi_react.py, run_react_infer.sh, prompt.py,
    tool_search.py, tool_visit.py, tool_scholar.py, tool_python.py, tool_file.py,
    file_tools/, eval_data/,
    judge/evaluate_deepsearch_official.py, judge/prompt.py

Our additions for this paper (the step-wise experience-injection evaluation):

    react_agent_step_wise.py, prompt_step_wise.py

The URL-blocking logic in tool_search.py / tool_visit.py is adapted from
MiroThinker. The agent depends on the Qwen-Agent library (qwen-agent on PyPI).
